    "name": "A Tiny Garden",
    "steam_appid": 3165880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165880/extras/4c5d3c74f1046b4b217ace76e844a603.avif?t=1771152491\" width=1056 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A Tiny Garden is a simple gardening/farming game which sits at the bottom of your screen. You can enjoy a movie or do something else while also playing the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165880/extras/1b7d184db7af02abb761662b79d1afcf.avif?t=1771152491\" width=1056 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Plant Crops, Bushes, Trees and Grains. Unlock different tiers and see which ones fits your style of gardening. If you don't care about cost and sale price, just plant whatever you like and have fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165880/extras/a2af165ecfb43bddff80f6466c0396dd.avif?t=1771152491\" width=1056 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Care for Chickens, Ducks and many more adorable creatures. Raise them in your tiny garden, give them their favorite food and get their unique produces</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165880/extras/cfafe21b3004f60b918773efaaa418fd.avif?t=1771152491\" width=1057 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Instead of selling your produce, process them into more expensive produce for higher price. Make jams, juices, breads, wine and many more. Do you want to go full on in with baking goods or Build your own winery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Design your perfect garden with endless possibilities. Grow Crops, Bushes, Trees and harvest them. Use those to feed your animals or process them into Jams, Pickles, Juices and Wines. Do all of that while watching your favorite movies and anime or while doing your work on your desktop.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
